I, like everyone else, initially thought there may be something amiss when I noticed the word, "Przedstawia," in the opening credits. For those that care, Przedstawia is Polish for Presents. However, that is the ONLY foreign language in this movie file. I watched the first 15 minutes of the movie as well as scanned the remaining portion of the movie, all dialogue is in ENGLISH.

This, coupled with the excellent quality of the video (1280*544), makes this an perfect find. Thank you uploader.
